{"service_name": "Security Advisory Service", "service_id": "7348561669983147", "company_name": "NCC Services Limited. Trading as NCC Group.", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     NCC Services Limited. Trading as NCC Group.\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Security Advisory Service\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    NCC Group is well placed to provide 360 degree security advice service to our clients in the wide range of areas. This includes all levels of security advice from the strategic to the detailed technical assistance: Strategy and Governance, Architecture reviews, Policy &amp; Procedure, Internal Audit and Compliance Programmes.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Full analysis of functional and non-functional requirements and compliance\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Formal report detailing the understanding\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Provision of CESG CHECK Accredited ITHC\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Assistance in development of appropriate firewall rules\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Penetration testing of service\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Strategic level direction\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Assessment of Information governance provision to date\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Understanding of organisations information security risk\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Understanding of the compliance requirements and approach required\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Report containing management summary with clear &amp; concise recommendation\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Experienced Information Assurance Consultant\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     CESG CLAS with IA Architect qualification\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     CESG CHECK certified ITHC\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Up-to-date with current trends\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Accessible, quality assured documentation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Knowledge sharing from world centre of excellence\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Information Security professional to provide ongoing service or advice\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Experienced&amp;qualified in the standards and issues that concern you\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Large pool of experience to call upon\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3120 per unit per hour\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Termination costs apply\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Hour\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/579474/7348561669983147-pricing-document-2015-10-04-2008.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/579474/7348561669983147-sfia-rate-card-2015-10-04-2008.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with